snippet: England captain Alastair Cook has not made any decision on whether to continue in the job, the 31-year-old said after his team's 4-0 series loss against India on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: England captain Alastair Cook has not made any decision on whether to continue in the job, the 31-year-old said after his team's 4-0 series loss against India on Tuesday.

headline.main: Captain Cook Yet to Decide on England Future
headline.print_headline: Captain Cook Yet to Decide on England Future
